title: HIIT BEYOND | LES MILLS GRIT x Reebok 30-minute HIIT workout
description:
Les Mills and Reebok have teamed up to bring you a free LES MILLS GRIT Cardio workout highlighting all the benefits of their first and only training shoe designed for high-intensity interval training! No equipment needed.
LES MILLS GRIT Cardio is a 30-minute HIIT workout that improves cardiovascular fitness, increases speed and maximizes calorie burn. Get ready to up the intensity. 

Try LES MILLS On Demand FREE for 14 days here: https://lmod.co/onlineworkouts

Try HIIT workouts at home on LES MILLS On Demand: https://www.lesmills.com/ondemand/workouts/hiit/
Find LES MILLS GRIT at a gym or club near you: https://www.lesmills.com/workouts/high-intensity-interval-training/?findaclass=

Shop the Reebok range: https://reebok.com/lesmills

Find GRIT on social: https://www.instagram.com/lesmillsgrit
Erin Maw, Trainer: https://instagram.com/erinmaw/
Ben Main, Trainer: https://instagram.com/imbenmain/
channelDescription:
Choose a workout you’ll actually enjoy with Les Mills 💚 Choose a science-backed, endorphin-raising workout from one of the happiest places on the planet: New Zealand.

Work out at a gym near you or at home with the LES MILLS+ app.

comments: I’ve literally done the “our lovely guest NINAAAA” workout dozens of times and it still challenges me so I’m excited to try this!!
I'm doing this as part of quarantine. I miss the gym but it's better to do this at home and be safe. Thank you Les Mills!

A co-worker and I (both teachers) put on our sneakers and did this workout with our students today at lunch time! We moved chairs and desks to the side and by the end we were all happy, exhausted and sweaty. Thanks for helping our Grade 7s get their physical activity in for the day, Les Mills!
The exercise and the trainers are out of this world but what makes this workout so much fun are their accents😂

The Nina workout have helped for so much , like I have been doing workouts from 4 years and found it difficult to loose weight but the Nina workout has made me loose 10 kgs over a year ( started Jan 10 & never missed a day) and toned my body so damm well & I started loving cardio and strength , I love that you have made another workout , looking found to loose more weight and tone my body , please make more workouts like this ✨✨✨✨
